        </p>
        <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold;">Support This Project</p>
          <p style="opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            Help maintain and host this archive
          </p>
