        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 1rem;">
          Documents are from public releases.
          <a href="https://github.com/epstein-docs/epstein-docs" style="color: #3498db; text-decoration: none;">Code is open source</a>.
